http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/Landscaping-to-be-done/article14004852.ece

Under the project, the zoo would be given facelift besides involving volunteers after capacity building as animal care givers, Mr. Vijay Kumar said.Total landscaping will be done besides building enclosures.The enclosures for primates built in 1970s have outlived and they have to be replaced with new one. Day and night crawling area has to be created. The veterinary hospital with in-patient facility has to be rebuilt besides providing digital X ray facility for big animals in their enclosures itself instead of bringing them to the hospital. Visitor amenities like benches, umbrella shelters, waiting rooms, parking lots and drinking network for animals and visitors as well as underground cabling will be taken up as part of the project.